MatchedRegions.transcript: So, what are autobidders or value maximizers?
Today, more than 80% of online advertising traffic involves autobidding.

MatchedRegion.Text: more than 80% of online advertising traffic involves autobidding

MatchedRegions.transcript: And most common alibators are target-driven, which means they want to get as many acquisitions or as much value as possible, subject to the constraint that the cost per acquisition or the return on investment ratio does not exceed a certain threshold.
In other words, autobidders want to maximize their value, subject to ROI constraints.
